casebody.data:
Leslie and Harlene ROBBINS, Respondents,
v.
MASON COUNTY TITLE, et al., Petitioners. No. 96726-1 Supreme Court of Washington. DATED at Olympia, Washington, May 2, 2019.

ORDER

¶ 1 This case came before the Court on its May 1, 2019, En Banc Conference to consider the petition for review. A majority of the Court voted in favor of the following result:

¶ 2 Now, therefore, it is hereby

¶ 3 ORDERED:

¶ 4 That the petition for review is granted. Review of the issue raised in the Respondents' answer to the petition is also granted. 

For the Court /s/ Fairhurst, CJ. CHIEF JUSTICE
